title: John Shirley - Halo Broken Circle
description: Centuries before the Human-Covenant War would rage across the galaxy, a similar conflict erupted between the Prophets and the ElitesÃ¢â‚¬â€two alien races at odds over the sacred artifacts left by the powerful Forerunners, who disappeared eons ago.
